  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238010/extras/49b0e01bbbf4d9b6e4e7826ea9dfb715.poster.avif?t=1702050970\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238010/extras/49b0e01bbbf4d9b6e4e7826ea9dfb715.webm?t=1702050970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238010/extras/49b0e01bbbf4d9b6e4e7826ea9dfb715.mp4?t=1702050970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Every now and then, the ocean hosts the most exciting and glorious competition ever created by fishkind : the The Great Lagoon Cup. This tournament of the first water, gathers countless competitive Bubble-eye hustlers from all around the ocean. <br><br>They like going by the name of <strong>Chiki-Chiki</strong>.<br>You might ask, “what is so special about this fishie-specie ?”<br><br>First of, they look fantastic. <br>Secondly, they can <strong>reach outstanding speed</strong> thanks to their strong native seahorse-power, at the cost of <strong>pretty challenging maneuverability</strong>. <br><br>Folks from far miles of sand came to witness first-class achievements, tragic yet comical events. And by fighting strong currents, entangled in seaweed, knocked away by coral turnstiles.. the fish with oversized cheeks will deliver, the best show ever. <br><br>The reefs are calling upon their new champion, and you just might have the chance of your life to take part.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238010/extras/7e053c5bb9ae5a63b058dbf229eec772.poster.avif?t=1702050970\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238010/extras/7e053c5bb9ae5a63b058dbf229eec772.webm?t=1702050970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238010/extras/7e053c5bb9ae5a63b058dbf229eec772.mp4?t=1702050970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Did someone say fishrace? </h2><br><strong>Yes we did.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238010/extras/e4111f4c5628d43a5e42ceb3d2c01e05.poster.avif?t=1702050970\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238010/extras/e4111f4c5628d43a5e42ceb3d2c01e05.webm?t=1702050970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238010/extras/e4111f4c5628d43a5e42ceb3d2c01e05.mp4?t=1702050970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Whether you’re here for <strong>Fun</strong> or for the <strong>Speedrun</strong>...</h2><br>To play Chiki-Chiki, you will need a controller with 2 joysticks to impulse your bubble-eye fish’s cheeks to victory.<br><br><strong>Easy to learn, awesome to master</strong>, the gameplay revolves around <strong>accuracy and physical simulations</strong>. Challenge everyone in this fun and frenzic 2D racing game, through a wide pan of crazy hurdles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What’s in the game?</h2><br>• Many <strong> gorgeous fishies</strong><br>• <strong>4</strong> colorful <strong>racing maps</strong><br>• <strong>Physic simulated environments</strong> filled with obstacles<br>• A <strong>local multiplayer 1v1</strong> game mode<br>• A <strong>single player time attack</strong> game mode <br>• <strong>Awesome soundtracks</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238010/extras/3e51a7d1128f00f2b9e15a54d17ec72c.poster.avif?t=1702050970\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238010/extras/3e51a7d1128f00f2b9e15a54d17ec72c.webm?t=1702050970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238010/extras/3e51a7d1128f00f2b9e15a54d17ec72c.mp4?t=1702050970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238010/extras/f95f0ad00c88aed7e5acc15956362cb3.avif?t=1702050970\" width=800 height=83 /></span>",
